<p>

She died of <disease wordnetid="114070360" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../539/243539.xml">
throat cancer</link></disease>
 in <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../110/18110.xml">
Los Angeles</link>, just a few weeks shy of her 80th birthday.</p>

